'''约瑟夫·顿谷鲁'''（{{lang-en|Joseph Ndunguru}}{{bd||}}）是一位[[坦桑尼亚|坦桑尼亚]]分子[[植物病毒|植物]][[病毒学|病毒学]]家<ref>{{Cite web|first=Kieron |last=Monks|title=Scientists battle 'Ebola of plants'|url=https://www.cnn.com/2017/07/11/africa/cassava-disease-east-africa/index.html|access-date=2020-06-24|website=CNN}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=The Great Tanzanian|url=http://tanzaniazalendo.org/our-nation/the-people/the-great-tanzanian/|access-date=2020-06-24|website=Tanzania Zalendo|language=en-US}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Joseph Ndunguru|url=http://www.cassavawhitefly.org/people/56-joseph-ndunguru|access-date=2020-06-24|website=www.cassavawhitefly.org}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|date=2017-08-07|title=Team|url=https://cassavavirusactionproject.com/team/|access-date=2020-06-24|website=Cassava Virus Action Project|language=en-US}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Meet the scientists {{!}} AgShare.Today|url=http://agshare.today/meet-the-scientists/|access-date=2020-06-24|language=en-US}}</ref>，主要从事分子水平理解植物病毒，并开发非洲重要经济作物病害的诊断工具<ref>{{Cite web|title=Joseph Ndunguru {{!}} Cassava Virus Evolution|url=https://www.cassavavirusevolution.org/content/joseph-ndunguru|access-date=2020-06-24|website=www.cassavavirusevolution.org}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Meet the BecA Hub staff - BecA-ILRI hub|url=http://hub.africabiosciences.org/aboutbeca/becahub-staff/114?view=person|access-date=2020-06-24|website=hub.africabiosciences.org}}</ref>。

